OL,3,CIFS warns of further tax rises
OL,4,Cfollowing chancellor's Spring Statement
OL,6,FThe chancellor says negative impact
OL,7,Fassessments of the reforms she
OL,8,Fannounced on Wednesday are based on a
OL,9,Ffalse premise
OL,11,FThe Institute for Fiscal Studies (IFS)
OL,12,Fhas warned the chancellor may need to
OL,13,Fraise taxes even further in the Autumn
OL,14,FBudget.
OL,16,FThis follows Rachel Reeves' Spring
OL,17,FStatement that aims to reduce the
OL,18,Fwelfare bill by nearly #5 billion.
