OL,3,CIFS warns of further tax rises
OL,4,Cfollowing chancellor's Spring Statement
OL,6,F"If it was right last week to announce
OL,7,Fa halving of the health component of
OL,8,Funiversal credit, it's hard to see why
OL,9,Fthis week it's right to do more than
OL,10,Fthat," Mr Johnson said.
OL,12,F"The worry for Ms Reeves is that
OL,13,Fheadroom remains very small indeed. We
OL,14,Flive in a risky and changing world.
OL,16,F"There's a good chance that economic
OL,17,Fand fiscal forecasts will deteriorate
OL,18,Fsignificantly between now and an
OL,19,FAutumn budget. If so she will need to
OL,20,Fcome back for more which will likely
OL,21,Fmean raising taxes even further."
