OL,6,FAsked about these risks, the
OL,7,FChancellor refused to be drawn on
OL,8,Fwhether there would be further cuts or
OL,9,Ftax raises come Autumn.
OL,11,F"I've said that we will meet our
OL,12,Ffiscal rules," she said.
OL,14,F"I am confident that the changes we're
OL,15,Fmaking to grow the economy is what is
OL,16,Fneeded both to improve living
OL,17,Fstandards, to meet our fiscal rules
OL,18,Fand crucially to have the money that
OL,19,Fis needed for our defence, schools and
OL,20,Fhospitals."
