OL,6,FThe chancellor denied cuts to welfare
OL,7,Fwould make people worse off, insisting
OL,8,Fthat assessments of her Spring
OL,9,FStatement were based on a false
OL,10,Fpremise that "no one will go back into
OL,11,Fwork."
OL,13,FShe said the whole point of these
OL,14,Fgovernment reforms is to move people
OL,15,Foff benefits and into work.
OL,17,F"We want to lift people out of poverty
OL,18,Fand give more people the opportunity
OL,19,Fto make a career," the chancellor said.
